                card.reseller_intro.actions_1.title: Back
                card.reseller_intro.body_0.text: Greentic Store — Sell AI Solutions
                card.reseller_intro.body_1.text: Join the marketplace for AI-powered solutions
                card.reseller_intro.body_2.text: The Greentic Store is a curated marketplace for ready-to-deploy AI solutions.
                card.reseller_intro.body_3.text: As a reseller, you can offer these solutions to your clients with full support.
                card.reseller_intro.body_4.text: Earn revenue through a transparent commission-based model.
